    <activity>
      <statement>
        <p>
          Solve this linear system using a matrix and row reduction.
          Describe the solution as a locus, as a span, and in a
          description by free parameters. 
          <md>
            <mrow>
              x - y + 2z \amp = 0 
            </mrow>
